# Splinter Cell: Blacklist, with Flydigi Apex 2 in mind.

# Movement
JoyXY WASD deadzone 30 ring 60 Shift
CamXY flick # Right Stick for turning
mousecalibration 1200 # Mouse units for one radian
flicktime 200
ingamemouse 1.0

# Triggers
TriggerR M1 # Fire
TriggerL M2 # Aim
# BumperL M3 # Ability
# BumperR G # Grenade
ActionL Shift # Sprint
ActionR E # Interact

ActionB Q # Cover
ActionA Space #  Use / Jump / Climb
